---
title: Sticky Grilled Lemongrass Tofu with Nutty Rice and Bright Mango Slaw
description: Aromatic lemongrass and sweet chilli-kissed grilled tofu is the highlight of this summery grill recipe! Perfectly paired with nutty rice and a bright mango slaw, what else could you ask for?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1007_W30_CA_RC23710-1_Maingrill_marks_edit_low-6142bff8.jpg
